{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"35efff",
"children":[
"Smoking cessation reduces all-cause mortality by up to 50%; ",
{
"type":"alert",
"children":[
"when it appears as a potential answer to a test question, it is almost always the correct choice."
]
}
]
}
]
},
