]
},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"0c5fbd",
"children":[
"The Five A's and the 5 R's are two motivational interviewing techniques to use when counseling for behavior change, including smoking cessation, at-risk drinking, and other substance use."
]
},
{
"type":"inline-wrap",
"wrapId":"1",
"contentIds":[
