"mk19_bb_gm_s20_inline_t2"
],
"forceOpen":true
},
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"e7e264",
"children":[
"Combination therapy is more effective than monotherapy."
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"ff0750",
"children":[
"Behavioral intervention and pharmacotherapy are more effective than either therapy used alone."
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"65d124",
"children":[
"Bupropion and varenicline can be used with long-acting (nicotine patches) or short-acting (nicotine gum, lozenges, inhalers, nasal spray) nicotine replacement."
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"c63c6d",
"children":[
"Combination nicotine replacement therapy (long- and short-acting nicotine replacement) is more effective than nicotine monotherapy."
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"heading",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
"Don't Be Tricked"
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"a22ed9",
"children":[
"Nicotine replacement therapy is not contraindicated following ",
{
"type":"abbreviation",
"title":"myocardial infarction",
"children":[
"MI"
]
},
" and can be started in the hospital."
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"0beabd",
"children":[
{
"type":"no-wrap",
"children":[
{
"type":"abbreviation",
"title":"selective serotonin reuptake inhibitor",
"children":[
"SSRI"
]
},
"s"
]
},
" show no significant benefit for smoking cessation."
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"3b35d1",
"children":[
"E-cigarettes are not approved by the FDA for smoking cessation."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
}
]
